<HEADLINE>
<P>
HERITAGE TO ACQUIRE LANDMARK THEATRE CORP. 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Heritage Entertainment Inc., Los Angeles, has agreed to acquire Landmark 
Theatre Corp., according to a filing with the Securities and Exchange 
Commission. 
</P>
<P>
Landmark will become a wholly owned subsidiary of Heritage. 
</P>
</TEXT>
