</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 San Francisco businessman Robert Setrakian has been elected chairman of the 
board of governors of the U.S. Postal Service. A member since 1985, Setrakian 
succeeds John Griesemer as head of the board, which oversees the operations of 
the Postal Service. Griesemer remains a member. 
</P>
