<TEXT>
<P>
Mayor Tom Bradley launched a bid for an unprecedented fifth term today, less 
than a week after his strongest potential challenger, City Councilman Zev 
Yaroslavsky, declared the mayor unbeatable and withdrew from contention. 
</P>
<P>
